    <h2 id="ï¸-project-of-the-day-ir-policy--tabletop-scenario">ğŸ› ï¸ Project of the Day: â€œIR Policy + Tabletop Scenarioâ€</h2>
    <p><strong>Scenario:</strong><br />
As the new security lead, youâ€™re asked to prepare the IR policy and run a tabletop simulation for an executive team.
<strong>Steps:</strong></p>
    <ol>
      <li>Draft 1-page IR policy for your organization</li>
      <li>Create a tabletop scenario (e.g., insider threat, stolen laptop, phishing attack)</li>
      <li>Define injects, decisions, escalation points</li>
      <li>Log what decisions teams make and reflect on response gaps
